lass=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"f8c0bbd1412b9e68044afa1042d6eabf92b68d20","tid":1561255,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:20:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d36f4e434f2dc1104098ef3f887c6c60ba5982ef","tid":1561255,"uid":25468,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:29:57.000Z","msg":"世柒的確燈力好強 , 有啲驚"},{"pid":"63f8916ef27a50bd4e3c36b6578a480863df3b68","tid":1561255,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:30:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d238a5ea048a243e79463da37071fcfa0cd4eb4","tid":1561255,"uid":71133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d36f4e434f2dc1104098ef3f887c6c60ba5982ef","tid":1561255,"uid":25468,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:29:57.000Z","msg":"世柒的確燈力好強 , 有啲驚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:32:36.000Z","msg":"僅次燒山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce0a2d88967752de434cfddc3d966a03d1745fa4","tid":1561255,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:42:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"304faa15cabae88403cdd3bdb528f4a750ae5d94","tid":1561255,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:49:23.000Z","msg":"香港政策法 已經發揮緊威力<br />\n2019-09-11 / by martinoei 黃世澤<br />\n據 Bloomberg 報導，一堆美國國會已經引用 香港政策法 賦<br />\n予國會權力，問商務部長同國務卿，香港有無用作中國偷美<br />\n國科技嘅白手套，以及果啲Crowd Control Agent有無被濫<br />\n用等問題。美國國會議員一邊推香港人權及民主法，一邊已<br />\n經發功要你香港政府死快啲。<br />\n香港政策法 發揮威力中<br />\n香港政策法 現行版本係弱，但由於當時美國已經驚中國利<br />\n用香港繞過巴黎統籌委員會嘅機制，係咁買科技威脅自由社<br />\n會，所以有以下條文<br />\n(6) signicant problems in cooperation between<br />\nHong Kong and the United States in the area of<br />\nexport controls;<br />\n所以呢次針對 Non-lethal Technologies ，以及香港有無做中<br />\n國買技術白手套呢啲問題，都係用export controls呢部分，<br />\n國務卿係有責任向外交事務委員會報告，所以要10月1日之<br />\n前覆機，美國已經係立即利用國會議員法定權力，去質問。<br />\n所以你話香港人權及民主法將會有幾強，國會成日要你<br />\nadministration交report，administration好多嘢都批唔到俾<br />\n你。<br />\n所以喺呢個背景下，我相信有兩個後果：<br />\n1. 美國啲公司一定唔可以再賣催淚彈同橡膠子彈俾香港，因為<br />\n為應付國會議員要求，可能要求有關公司做大量<br />\npaperwork，又唔係十分之好賺，做嚟把叉咩。<br />\n2. 以後好多科技，都會好難再賣俾香港，香港大專院校，亦好<br />\n難再同美國或歐盟嘅機構合作，因為怕呢個白手套問題，學<br />\n術機構好多買嘅儀器、軟件，或掂嘅技術，都要相應美國出<br />\n口管制豁免或牌照，所以依家商務部同國務院都費時批俾<br />\n你，否則寫薯仔文寫唔完。<br />\n當然，Marco Rubio 已經發緊功，表明推香港人權及民主法<br />\n案，因為始終現行 香港政策法 係威力唔夠，否則點解要香<br />\n港人權及民主法案呢？<br />\nThe most important thing Congress can<br />\ndo is pass Sen Marco Rubio&rsquo;s Hong Kong<br />\nHuman Rights and Democracy Act.<br />\n#China&rsquo;s efforts to control #HongKong<br />\ndemonstrates the need for an annual<br />\nevaluation of Hong Kong&rsquo;s special status.<br />\n<a href=\"http://pic.twitter.com/vkYwgCUwLk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.twitter.com%2FvkYwgCUwLk&d=y6uglPlKbSLkZz%2BcPL4okcjWZIlHEnPb%2Ft7norCwxRo%3D&h=780ea24f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">pic.twitter.com/vkYwgCUwLk</a><br />\n&mdash; Senator Rubio Press (@SenRubioPress)<br />\nSeptember 10, 2019<br />\n所以依家香港商界應該打緊冷震，Amazon已經嚴審香港廠<br />\n商政治背景，梗係收到風，或美國嘅律師聞到有味，幫個客<br />\n搞掂呢啲嘢。香港商界如果仲喺幫中共，我諗你哋班友真係<br />\n同中共攬炒，香港人其實對攬炒無所謂。我唔明點解梁文道<br />\n咁驚攬炒就係。<br />\n後話：自美國介入有效後，某個成成日鬧人唔好要依靠外國人<br />\n搞香港自治嘅組織，飛撲嚟美國人啲Twitter度，然後熱狗<br />\n又喺度話我係燒山一樣嘅燈神。我有燒山嘅燈力，我一早用<br />\n嚟買德國Lotto 6 aus 49中頭獎發咗，仲益你班冚家鏟。我有<br />\n燈力，留番俾自己用好過喇，講嚟講去，黃洋達、陳秀慧呢<br />\n啲人渣，都係一班賊。熱普城死全家，我都係果句。"},{"pid":"200343344cf6baee6d826a114af48cc72d55ab3c","tid":1561255,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:50:44.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n針對中立淺藍黃嘅文宣【牆紙！】<br />\n第四期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1547783/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1547783/page/1</a><br />\n第三期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1519434/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1519434/page/1</a><br />\n第二期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1498347/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1498347/page/1</a><br />\n第一期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1479130/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1479130/page/1</a><br />\nTG CHANNEL :<a href=\"https://t.me/WallPaperENews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FWallPaperENews&d=y6uglPlKbSLkZz%2BcPL4okcjWZIlHEnPb%2Ft7norCwxRo%3D&h=717ec2cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/WallPaperENews</a>"},{"pid":"83fdd30ada32f2830a8f268e943f8355f8a99850","tid":1561255,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T15:04:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8b58c72f0609a78a805f2e28b969a98f5cc0dc6","tid":1561255,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T15:13:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3b33e71fff6a8e43ea578f5661703d2d1b0b6a3","tid":1561255,"uid":34334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T15:19:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bbe4c8ae036092847e23486dd5007139da44ca43","tid":1561255,"uid":47198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T15:21:21.000Z"